# === AI-agent guidance & scratch ===
# AGENTS.md, CLAUDE.md, and .claude/{rules,skills,agents} are tracked public
# agent guidance. Everything else under .claude/ stays ignored by default
# (settings.local.json, worktrees/ runtime state, *.lock, anything dropped
# there by habit). Session notes, handoffs, audits, and private working files
# live in scratch/ — never commit. .agents/ holds legacy Codex-format skills
# (unused, kept local).
scratch/
.claude/*
!.claude/rules/
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/agents/
.agents/
.codex
docs/kernel-config-reference/
dev/
docs/signature.rst
scripts/kernel-hardening-check-build.sh
scripts/kernel-hardening-check-target.sh
scripts/generate-splash.py
scripts/tpm-validate.sh
